{"tid":1693330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉淑儀：律政司「甩碌」令人氣憤","createTime":"2019-11-04T14:05:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T15:53:40.000Z","uid":254923,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3e998dc74d67460301567d282566a52730b84199","tid":1693330,"uid":254923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:05:55.000Z","msg":"【律政司「甩碌」令人氣憤】<br />\n<br />\n傍晚收到許多市民WhatsApp及電郵 ，以及朋友來電查詢，他們均對於警方搗破灣仔軍火武器庫的案件，律政司因「擺烏龍」寫錯被告姓名及控罪，以致涉藏逾百汽油彈的五名被告獲釋(其後警方已於庭外再次拘捕)，表示憤怒及大惑不解。<br />\n<br />\n此案是經過警方多番偵查及專業搜證，從而拘捕疑犯，將其緝拿歸案。假如案件因為律政司「甩碌」而被逼撤銷控罪，讓疑犯有機會逍遙法外的話，真的令人十分氣憤。不少人更詢問當中是否有其他內情？我表示明天見到律政司司長時，會當面向她查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UdMsFKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUdMsFKW.jpg&h=61d033ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9738bc6b71033ea73c5d0dfbed7d43ad2d1a5e8c","tid":1693330,"uid":254923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:06:25.000Z","msg":"反了反了，面都唔比了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e3f2467592899c60bf8ef33af1935433e62c8","tid":1693330,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:16:49.000Z","msg":"開始跑馬仔了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461255f0b0969d00e52e93595a51f96191db54bb","tid":1693330,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:17:37.000Z","msg":"鄭藥華反了"},{"pid":"c517cf52052c4d9110cde068fb4b9f0970ec3569","tid":1693330,"uid":94344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"想保住份工而又有罷工效果？輪更制幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n樽頸？攬炒？不如試下輪更啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1693297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1693297</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"232a4adad146a7138a0f60ec994bcf170ec75057","tid":1693330,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T1